            {
                  try
                  {
                        $OriginalFilePath = str_replace( '/./' , '/' , $OriginalFilePath );
                        $Data = $this->Cache->get_data( $OriginalFilePath );
                        if( $Data !== false )
                        {
                              return( $Data );
                        }
                        else
                        {
                              $Data = @file_get_contents( $OriginalFilePath );
                              if( $Data !== false )
                              {
                                    $this->Cache->add_data( $OriginalFilePath , $Data );
